Package: combodesign
Title: Component-Contribution Design for Drug Combination Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miles", family = "Xi", email = "nxi@ucla.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Miles Xi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Miles Xi <nxi@ucla.edu>
Description: Implements one-sided component-contribution operating
    characteristics, joint-power sample-size calculations, and allocation
    comparisons for three-arm drug combination trials with component arms A
    and B and combination arm AB.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    mvtnorm,
    stats
